     * @link https://github.com/jagenjo/litegl.js/blob/master/src/mesh.js
     * 
     * @param {Prim} the Prim needing geometry. 
     * @returns {Prim.geometry} geometry data, including vertices, indices, normals, texture coords and tangents. 
